tool_description: The Movies API is a comprehensive solution for integrating entertainment data into applications, offering detailed information on movies and TV shows across various streaming platforms. It provides APIs for retrieving detailed information about specific shows and movies, searching for content based on criteria like genre or actor, and accessing categorized lists of trending and new releases. Each API delivers rich metadata, including images, release dates, genres, synopses, and availability on platforms like Netflix, Prime, Disney, HBO, and Hulu. This tool enhances user discovery and engagement by enabling detailed content exploration and seamless access to streaming services.
head: https://movies-api14.p.rapidapi.com

tool_description: OTT Details is a comprehensive API service designed to provide extensive information about movies and TV shows across various streaming platforms. It supports over 150 streaming services, 25 genres, and 320 languages, with data updated daily. The tool offers multiple endpoints to facilitate advanced searches, retrieve detailed movie and TV show information, filter content by genre and language, and access lists of supported streaming services. Key functionalities include searching by IMDB ID or movie title, filtering by release year, IMDb rating, genre, and language, and retrieving detailed information such as cast bios, user reviews, plot summaries, and streaming availability. The API also supports fetching new arrivals, additional title details including reviews and quotes, and basic information about actors and their notable works.
head: https://ott-details.p.rapidapi.com

tool_description: Advanced Movie Search is a tool designed to facilitate comprehensive movie searches by various criteria such as genre, name, and detailed information retrieval. It offers APIs to list movie genres, search movies by genre or name, and fetch detailed information about specific movies, including budget, revenue, and production details. This tool is ideal for users and applications requiring detailed movie data for filtering, browsing, and analysis.
head: https://advanced-movie-search.p.rapidapi.com

tool_description: Anime DB is a comprehensive tool designed to provide detailed information about anime titles. It offers APIs to retrieve all anime details with pagination, list genres for categorizing media, fetch specific anime by ranking, and get comprehensive details about an anime using its unique identifier. These functionalities make it suitable for applications requiring detailed anime content data, such as recommendation systems or databases.
head: https://anime-db.p.rapidapi.com
